    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/c67e148c273042311068d9ee165b7257.poster.avif?t=1684064895\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/c67e148c273042311068d9ee165b7257.webm?t=1684064895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/c67e148c273042311068d9ee165b7257.mp4?t=1684064895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dubspace revolves around physical interactions that rely on forces and impulses. Mailcom navigates the zero-gravity environment using his jetpack, as well as weapons, pushing and pulling objects and obstacles. He may move fast, but he must be careful.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/19af63dcb61061a16ecb5bc5089d508b.poster.avif?t=1684064895\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/19af63dcb61061a16ecb5bc5089d508b.webm?t=1684064895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/19af63dcb61061a16ecb5bc5089d508b.mp4?t=1684064895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Mailcom will explore dark and foreboding space stations, each with its own unique environment and set of challenges. These stations are filled with obstacles, traps, and other hazards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/1f5a1db94c8fe640deb4d5d4b7899919.poster.avif?t=1684064895\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/1f5a1db94c8fe640deb4d5d4b7899919.webm?t=1684064895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/1f5a1db94c8fe640deb4d5d4b7899919.mp4?t=1684064895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Launching a heavy object into the path of an enemy, redirecting the projectile with a well-timed push or solving an environmental puzzle, players must make use of properties such as mass and bounciness to their advantage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/f52d941a3ba0fa6922452dbec532fc1a.poster.avif?t=1684064895\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/f52d941a3ba0fa6922452dbec532fc1a.webm?t=1684064895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/f52d941a3ba0fa6922452dbec532fc1a.mp4?t=1684064895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enemies come in many forms and shapes, spawned in a variety of ways to create endless combat situations. With a choice of weapons, grenades and items at their disposal, players can eliminate enemies in any way they see fit.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/9124d057d7d3c3a87ad3fadac9ea3fda.poster.avif?t=1684064895\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/9124d057d7d3c3a87ad3fadac9ea3fda.webm?t=1684064895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2342480/extras/9124d057d7d3c3a87ad3fadac9ea3fda.mp4?t=1684064895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>NOTE: Controller is required for local multiplayer",
